    "breadcrumb": "Introduction \u003e What's New \u003e Version 5",
    "content": "5.1.0 (2022-07-15) Hugo 0.95.0 0.95.0 This release requires a newer Hugo version. Change Change Because the print preview URLs were non deterministic for normal pages in comparison to page bundles, this is now changed. Each print preview is now accessible by adding a index.print.html to the default URL.\nYou can revert this behavior by overwriting the print output format setting in your hugo.tomlto:\nhugo. toml yaml json [outputFormats] [outputFormats.print] baseName = 'index' isHTML = true mediaType = 'text/html' name = 'print' path = '_print' permalinkable = false outputFormats: print: baseName: index isHTML: true mediaType: text/html name: print path: _print permalinkable: false { \"outputFormats\": { \"print\": { \"baseName\": \"index\", \"isHTML\": true, \"mediaType\": \"text/html\", \"name\": \"print\", \"path\": \"_print\", \"permalinkable\": false } } }",
